      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Oh sure they should be fixed upstream; but I'd rather this be manually edited once to at least have _a_ submission for the tapeout slot filed that isn't expected to be buggy by best understanding at the time of filing, than to risk something happeneing like idk even jst one's computer releasing magic smoke and ending up without any expected-functional submission filed.",
